data.description: Charming mid-century single-owner ranch home in the heart of Longmont. This property has been lovingly maintained and boasts a treasure trove of recent improvements that blend classic flair with modern comfort. Inside, you'll be greeted by a seamless open-concept living and dining area, adorned with recently updated carpets. The spacious kitchen has plenty of storage and counter space for all of your culinary needs. 3 bedrooms are adorned with hardwood floors.  The family area is designed for warmth and relaxation, featuring a wood stove nestled on a brick hearth. Curl up with a book, a cup of cocoa, or simply bask in the glow of the fire's embrace. The spacious office area provides the perfect setting to work from home, pursue hobbies, or transform the space into an extra bedroom or creative sanctuary. Outside, the spacious fenced backyard features an inviting brick patio, perfect for sun-soaked brunches and moonlit conversations. The detached garage has been transformed into a heated workshop, a haven for crafters and tinkerers to bring their creative visions to life. With easy access to downtown, walking trails, shopping,  restaurants, and Lefthand Brewing this home embodies the essence of convenience. No HOA.
